== slim :breadcrumb

div role="main"
  .headerless
  h1.aligned-title Layouts
  p These layouts are examples of how we use the design system for common pages across the university. You can filter them by <em>status</em> and <em>category</em>. The status of a layout is one of:
  ul
    li
      strong> Prototype
      | - the layout is being actively developed and is not yet ready for use.
    li
      strong> Stable
      ' - the layout is ready for use; if you notice any issue please
      a href="https://github.com/marcom-unimelb/unimelb-design-system/issues" let us know
      | .
    li
      strong> Deprecated
      | - the layout should no longer be used, as it will be removed in the next major release of the design system.
  p.alert-info
    strong> Tip:
    | view the raw source of any layout by adding <code>/source</code> to the end of its URL.
  
  section
    .filtered-listing-wrapper.alt
      form.filtered-listing-select
        fieldset.left
          legend Filter by status:
          div.all
            input.checkbox type="checkbox" name="f[degree_type]" checked="checked" data-tag="all" id="c00"
            label for="c00" tabindex="0"
              span All
          div.category-e
            input#c1.checkbox type="checkbox" name="f[course_type]" data-tag="category-e"
            label for="c1" tabindex="0"
              span Prototype
          div.category-a
            input#c2.checkbox type="checkbox" name="f[course_type]" data-tag="category-a"
            label for="c2" tabindex="0"
              span Stable
          div.category-b
            input#c3.checkbox type="checkbox" name="f[course_type]" data-tag="category-b"
            label for="c3" tabindex="0"
              span Deprecated
        .right
          label for="f-select2" Filter by category:
          div
            select#f-select2.alt name="f[select2]"
              option value="-1" All categories
              option value="website-sections" Website sections
              option value="news" News
              option value="events" Events
              option value="articles" Articles
              option value="linked-listing" Linked Listings
              option value="staff" Staff
              option value="de-co-branded" De/co-branded
              option value="server-pages" Server pages

